title: Repaint! Kay Wren the Witch in Training ☆ Halloween Collaboration 2021
author: Dollightful
description:
Happy Halloween, everyone! Say hello to our cute new addition to the Halloween Dolls line up, the young witch-in-training, Kay Wren!

The Halloween 2021 Playlist: https://youtube.com/playlist?list=PLwf5az3O7M4ckG0_-VZqqgsR7gXUcWaXu

Collaboration Partners: 
@Valkitty'sWorld  
@The Dolly Geek 
@Mr. Super Customs 
@Moonlight Jewel 
@Kyros Workshop 
@JackyOhhh 
@HeXtian 
@H ALI Crafts 
@etellan 
@Enchanterium 
@Anastazia Custom 

--------------------------------------------
The witch hatch template (US letter size): https://drive.google.com/file/d/1SSJi7u6zFHLCx2vCplL4__oTQApD0cr5/view?usp=sharing 

The witch hatch template (A4 size): https://drive.google.com/file/d/1RN5PJQnXnk2kgER_VFGMK9F6IoFudbjB/view?usp=sharing
--------------------------------------------
Merchandise:
https://www.zazzle.com/store/dollightful/collections
https://society6.com/dollightful
Doll clothing patterns here: https://www.etsy.com/shop/DollightfulPatterns
Instagram, Twitter, Pinterest: @dollightfully
-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
MATERIALS:
Monster High Doll – “Howleen Wolf”
Nylon doll hair from http://www.dollyhair.com/
Reroot tool and needles from https://www.etsy.com/shop/thedollplanethair/
Pastels - Mungyo Hand-Rolled Soft Pastels
Water Colored Pencils - Faber Castell
Mr.Super Clear UV Flat (wear a mask and spray in a ventilated area!)
Mask - Organic Vapor Particle Respirator Mask
Acrylic paint (Liquitex, Alpha)
Varnish (Duraclear)
Polymer clay (Sculpey)
--------------------------------------------
Musical tracks from:
Artlist https://artlist.io 
Dance of the Lunar Witch by Yonnie Dror
Dreamland by Spearfisher
Slippery Customer, Sneaky Tricks by Matt Stewart Evans
The One-Eyed Captain, Turtle Blues, Mad Crows by Ian Post
Ghost Waltz, Midnight Escape by Ziv Moran
-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Additional images from https://www.shutterstock.com
